https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=24950	6840
Google<a href="http://googleblog.blogspot.com/2011/07/first-google-ebooks-integrated-e-reader.html">宣布</a>将在7月17日<a href="http://arstechnica.com/gadgets/news/2011/07/140-google-ebooks-reader-iriver-story-hd-hits-stores-july-17.ars">发布</a>一款Google eBook阅读器iriver Story HD。<i>
